  77,46,"Yidlani\tnizithokozise\tokwesikhashana\tngempela\tnina niyizigebengu"
  77,47,Usizi ngalolosuku kwabaphikayo
  77,48,"Futhi uma kuthiwa kubona, “khothamani” abakhothami"
  77,49,Usizi ngalolosuku kwabaphikayo
  77,50,Ngakho-ke iyiphi inkulumo abayoyikholwa emva kwayo